# ZenZone App System Requirements

Here are the features and the functions of the ZenZone app system. there have two main types. They are functional and non-functional requirements. 

## Functional Requirements

For Functional requirements, 

- Users log in and create account 
- find buddy
- create and find the study rooms
- chat with study partners in the room
- add study goals and tasks
- track study sessions and productivity statistics

## Non-Functional Requirements

For non- functional requirements,

- The system support multiple users studying simultaneously.
- The interface is reliable and user friendly.
- The system load within 3 seconds.
- User data are being secure and protected.
- The system is accessible on web and mobile browsers.
